{"title":"故乡情思（二首）","authors":["阿红"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡情思（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别惊破我的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有这朝霞似的高粱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有这绿海似的大豆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池边，也有白鹅把长颈抿在翅下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头，也有翠柳多情地掩着井口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难得听到机械的响声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是慢腾腾的黄牛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有些姑娘还穿着偏襟衣裳绣花鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老太太脑后还挽着疙瘩鬏……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的家乡好象在天之涯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一合眼，却就落身村头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司机同志，请且慢鸣响喇叭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别惊破我的梦，我的神游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡虽然有些陈旧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我分明见它昂起了头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新楼的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新楼落成了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象出浴的美人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婷婷玉立在绿毯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这多的眼睛看她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她竟有点害羞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽一朵白云遮脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新楼的母亲——我们的老工程师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎面手扶梧桐树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白眉下笑眯着眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那神态，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活象一位少妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端详孩儿的颜面！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}